Wabiga jubba waa wabiga koowaad ee ugu wayn dalka [[somalia]] waana wabi aad ubalaaran .
Waxaa uu ka soo bilaawdaa wadanka [[Ethiopia]] sida wabiga kale ee [[Shabeele]], wabigaan waxoo dalka ka soo galaa gobolka [[Doolow]] wuxuuna gaaraa ilaa iyo magaalada [[kismaayo]] meelaha uu marana waa meelaha ogu taajirsan wadanka Somalia waana dhul beereedyo ah.

